There are currently not many items in each of the chests. Just to give you an idea of the sort of treasure you might get only single note is held with in each of the containers. Open up the toolset and add other items if you wish. Also note that you might just not get anything from killing the dryads, all of this is explained in the x0_i0_treasure script, open it and take some time to read it please.

Any questions and comments, post them at: http://p2.forumforfree.com/shayan.html

Hope it is useful -- Shayan.
This three-tined variation of a spear is a favored weapon of some undersea humanoids.
Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.
Low and flat, this chest seems to have been designed for the storage and filing of a merchant's accounts.
